st-faction-relations-program-name = Отношения группировок

# Relation type display names
st-faction-relations-type-alliance = Союз
st-faction-relations-type-neutral = Нейтралитет
st-faction-relations-type-hostile = Конфликт
st-faction-relations-type-war = Война

# Lore-friendly broadcast variants (picked at random)
# Alliance announcements
st-faction-relations-alliance-1 = Сталкеры, новости из надежного источника. {$factionA} и {$factionB} пожали друг-другу руки. Теперь они союзники.
st-faction-relations-alliance-2 = Слушайте сюда. {$factionA} и {$factionB} заключили соглашение. Союз. Это должно поменять расклад сил в Зоне.
st-faction-relations-alliance-3 = Срочные новости. {$factionA} и {$factionB} решили действовать вместе. Если вы не с ними, то лучше будьте начеку.
st-faction-relations-alliance-4 = По радио понеслись сплетни. {$factionA} и {$factionB} начали работать сообща. Будь начеку.

# Neutral announcements
st-faction-relations-neutral-1 = Похоже {$factionA} и {$factionB} разрядили обстановку между собой и вернулись к нейтралитету.
st-faction-relations-neutral-2 = Слышал у костра, что {$factionA} и {$factionB} договорились о прекращении огня. Пока что.
st-faction-relations-neutral-3 = {$factionA} и {$factionB} уладили конфликты. Отношения вновь нейтральны. Не рекомендую никому расчитывать, что продлиться долго.
st-faction-relations-neutral-4 = До меня дошли слухи, что {$factionA} и {$factionB} объявили перемирие.

# Hostile announcements
st-faction-relations-hostile-1 = Ушки на макушки. {$factionA} и {$factionB} снова втянулись в конфликт. Патрули у них могут быть нервными.
st-faction-relations-hostile-2 = Конфликт между {$factionA} и {$factionB}. Не завидую тем, кто оказался между ними.
st-faction-relations-hostile-3 = Внимание, сталкеры. {$factionA} и {$factionB} погрызлись меж собой. Держитесь подальше от их территорий.
st-faction-relations-hostile-4 = Между {$factionA} и {$factionB} разгорелся конфликт и настроеные они враждебно. Сейчас возле их территорий может быть неразбериха.

# War announcements
st-faction-relations-war-1 = Так, а это уже серьёзно. {$factionA} и {$factionB} находятся в состоянии войны. Держитесь подальше от линии фронта, если не хотите оказаться в мешке для трупов.
st-faction-relations-war-2 = Полномасштабная война между {$factionA} и {$factionB}. Стреляют друг в друга без предупреждений. Если жизнь дорога — держитесь подальше.
st-faction-relations-war-3 = Зона снова стала ещё опаснее. {$factionA} и {$factionB} объявили о войне. Кровь будет литься рекой.
st-faction-relations-war-4 = Война между {$factionA} и {$factionB}. Они стреляют во все, что движется у их позиций. Тебя предупредили, сталкер.

# =============================================
# Proposal sent announcements
# =============================================

# Alliance proposal sent
st-faction-relations-proposal-alliance-1 = Говорят, {$factionA} протянула руку помощи {$factionB}. Они предлагают заключить союз. Посмотрим, согласится ли {$factionB} на предложение.
st-faction-relations-proposal-alliance-2 = Interesting development. {$factionA} wants to ally with {$factionB}. The ball is in their court now.
st-faction-relations-proposal-alliance-3 = {$factionA} is looking for friends in the Zone. They sent an alliance offer to {$factionB}. Could change everything if they agree.
st-faction-relations-proposal-alliance-4 = Heard some chatter. {$factionA} proposed a full alliance to {$factionB}. The Zone holds its breath.

# Neutral proposal sent
st-faction-relations-proposal-neutral-1 = Seems like {$factionA} wants to bury the hatchet with {$factionB}. They are proposing neutral terms. Whether {$factionB} agrees is another story.
st-faction-relations-proposal-neutral-2 = {$factionA} sent a peace offer to {$factionB}. They want to go neutral. Not sure {$factionB} is ready to forgive and forget.
st-faction-relations-proposal-neutral-3 = A trader told me {$factionA} reached out to {$factionB} for a ceasefire. Neutral terms on the table. Time will tell.
st-faction-relations-proposal-neutral-4 = {$factionA} is tired of fighting {$factionB}, it seems. They proposed going neutral. Now we wait for an answer.

# Hostile proposal sent
st-faction-relations-proposal-hostile-1 = {$factionA} wants to dial things down with {$factionB}. They are proposing to step back from war to hostile. Still tense, but less shooting.
st-faction-relations-proposal-hostile-2 = Heard that {$factionA} is looking to ease off on {$factionB}. Proposing hostile terms instead of open war. We will see if {$factionB} agrees.
st-faction-relations-proposal-hostile-3 = {$factionA} sent word to {$factionB}. They want to pull back from full war, keep it at hostile. Both sides still armed, just less trigger-happy.
st-faction-relations-proposal-hostile-4 = Interesting. {$factionA} proposed to {$factionB} that they stop the war and settle on hostile terms. Could save some lives if they accept.

# War proposal sent
st-faction-relations-proposal-war-1 = This is grim. {$factionA} just sent {$factionB} what amounts to a declaration of war. Awaiting their response.
st-faction-relations-proposal-war-2 = {$factionA} proposed war with {$factionB}. That is not something you hear every day. The Zone tenses up.
st-faction-relations-proposal-war-3 = Reports say {$factionA} wants all-out war with {$factionB}. The proposal is on the table. Things could get very ugly.
st-faction-relations-proposal-war-4 = Disturbing news from the campfire. {$factionA} sent a war proposal to {$factionB}. If they accept, blood will flow.

# =============================================
# Proposal accepted announcements
# =============================================

# Alliance accepted
st-faction-relations-accepted-alliance-1 = It is official. {$factionB} accepted {$factionA}'s alliance offer. Those two are brothers in arms now. The Zone shifts.
st-faction-relations-accepted-alliance-2 = {$factionB} shook hands with {$factionA}. Alliance confirmed. If you are on their bad side, you just got twice the trouble.
st-faction-relations-accepted-alliance-3 = Good news or bad news, depends on where you stand. {$factionB} agreed to ally with {$factionA}. Big power move.
st-faction-relations-accepted-alliance-4 = The deal is done. {$factionB} accepted the alliance from {$factionA}. The balance of power just shifted, stalker.

# Neutral accepted
st-faction-relations-accepted-neutral-1 = {$factionB} accepted {$factionA}'s peace offer. They are neutral now. A rare moment of sanity in the Zone.
st-faction-relations-accepted-neutral-2 = Ceasefire confirmed. {$factionB} agreed to neutral terms with {$factionA}. Do not expect it to last forever though.
st-faction-relations-accepted-neutral-3 = {$factionB} took {$factionA}'s olive branch. Relations are neutral. The guns are quiet, for now.
st-faction-relations-accepted-neutral-4 = Peace in the Zone. Well, sort of. {$factionB} went neutral with {$factionA}. I would still watch my back around both of them.

# Hostile accepted
st-faction-relations-accepted-hostile-1 = {$factionB} agreed to step down from war with {$factionA}. They are hostile now, not at war. Still dangerous, but less carnage.
st-faction-relations-accepted-hostile-2 = The war between {$factionA} and {$factionB} is winding down. {$factionB} accepted hostile terms. Still tense, but the bullets slowed down.
st-faction-relations-accepted-hostile-3 = {$factionB} accepted {$factionA}'s proposal. They went from war to hostile. Progress, I suppose, if you can call it that.
st-faction-relations-accepted-hostile-4 = The shooting has eased up. {$factionB} agreed to hostile terms with {$factionA} instead of full war. Still not friends though.

# War accepted
st-faction-relations-accepted-war-1 = {$factionB} accepted {$factionA}'s war declaration. It is on. Full-scale conflict. Stay away from the frontlines.
st-faction-relations-accepted-war-2 = War is official. {$factionB} met {$factionA}'s challenge head-on. Expect heavy fighting across the Zone.
st-faction-relations-accepted-war-3 = No surprise there. {$factionB} answered {$factionA}'s war proposal with a war of their own. Blood will flow freely now.
st-faction-relations-accepted-war-4 = Both sides are committed. {$factionB} accepted war with {$factionA}. The Zone just got a lot more deadly, brothers.

# =============================================
# Proposal rejected announcements
# =============================================

# Alliance rejected
st-faction-relations-rejected-alliance-1 = {$factionB} turned down {$factionA}'s alliance offer. Trust is hard to come by in the Zone.
st-faction-relations-rejected-alliance-2 = No deal. {$factionB} rejected the alliance proposal from {$factionA}. Business as usual in the Zone.
st-faction-relations-rejected-alliance-3 = {$factionB} was not interested in {$factionA}'s friendship. Alliance rejected. Some grudges run deep.
st-faction-relations-rejected-alliance-4 = {$factionA} tried to ally with {$factionB}, but got turned down cold. The Zone remains divided.

# Neutral rejected
st-faction-relations-rejected-neutral-1 = {$factionB} rejected {$factionA}'s peace offer. They are not ready to forgive. The conflict continues.
st-faction-relations-rejected-neutral-2 = No ceasefire today. {$factionB} turned down {$factionA}'s neutral proposal. Too much bad blood, it seems.
st-faction-relations-rejected-neutral-3 = {$factionA} wanted peace with {$factionB}, but the answer was no. Expect the fighting to continue.
st-faction-relations-rejected-neutral-4 = {$factionB} spit on {$factionA}'s ceasefire offer. Peace is not on the menu today, stalker.

# Hostile rejected
st-faction-relations-rejected-hostile-1 = {$factionB} refused to de-escalate with {$factionA}. They want to keep things as they are. No stepping back.
st-faction-relations-rejected-hostile-2 = {$factionA} tried to cool things down with {$factionB}, but no luck. The current status holds.
st-faction-relations-rejected-hostile-3 = {$factionB} is not interested in {$factionA}'s de-escalation offer. The situation remains unchanged.
st-faction-relations-rejected-hostile-4 = No deal between {$factionA} and {$factionB}. The hostility proposal was rejected. Things stay the way they are.

# War rejected
st-faction-relations-rejected-war-1 = {$factionB} rejected {$factionA}'s war declaration. They are not taking the bait. At least not yet.
st-faction-relations-rejected-war-2 = {$factionA} wanted war with {$factionB}, but {$factionB} refused to engage. Tensions remain, but no open conflict.
st-faction-relations-rejected-war-3 = Interesting. {$factionB} turned down {$factionA}'s call for war. Cooler heads prevailed, for now.
st-faction-relations-rejected-war-4 = {$factionB} declined {$factionA}'s war proposal. The Zone holds its breath, but no shots fired today.

# =============================================
# Proposal expired announcements
# =============================================

# Alliance expired
st-faction-relations-expired-alliance-1 = Word on the radio is {$factionA}'s alliance offer to {$factionB} went unanswered. The deal is dead, stalker.
st-faction-relations-expired-alliance-2 = {$factionA} waited too long for {$factionB} to accept the alliance. The offer has expired. Back to business as usual.
st-faction-relations-expired-alliance-3 = That alliance proposal from {$factionA} to {$factionB}? Time ran out. Guess trust is in short supply around here.
st-faction-relations-expired-alliance-4 = {$factionA}'s hand stayed empty. {$factionB} never shook it. The alliance proposal expired in silence.

# Neutral expired
st-faction-relations-expired-neutral-1 = {$factionA}'s peace offer to {$factionB} expired. Silence speaks louder than bullets sometimes.
st-faction-relations-expired-neutral-2 = No response from {$factionB} on {$factionA}'s ceasefire proposal. The offer is off the table.
st-faction-relations-expired-neutral-3 = That neutral proposal from {$factionA} to {$factionB}? Dead in the water. Too slow, too late.
st-faction-relations-expired-neutral-4 = {$factionA} wanted peace with {$factionB}, but the clock ran out. No deal, stalker.

# Hostile expired
st-faction-relations-expired-hostile-1 = {$factionA}'s de-escalation offer to {$factionB} expired. The war drums keep beating.
st-faction-relations-expired-hostile-2 = {$factionB} never responded to {$factionA}'s proposal to ease tensions. The conflict continues as is.
st-faction-relations-expired-hostile-3 = Time ran out on {$factionA}'s offer to {$factionB}. Looks like neither side wanted to blink first.
st-faction-relations-expired-hostile-4 = That de-escalation proposal from {$factionA}? Expired. {$factionB} did not even acknowledge it.

# War expired
st-faction-relations-expired-war-1 = {$factionA}'s war declaration to {$factionB} expired without response. An uneasy quiet settles over the Zone.
st-faction-relations-expired-war-2 = {$factionB} ignored {$factionA}'s call to war. The challenge has expired. For now.
st-faction-relations-expired-war-3 = No answer from {$factionB} on {$factionA}'s war proposal. The declaration has lapsed.
st-faction-relations-expired-war-4 = {$factionA} wanted war with {$factionB}, but the proposal expired. Maybe cooler heads prevailed after all.

